  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introdução a LAME</title>

    <para>
      The <application>LAME</application> package contains an MP3 encoder and
optionally, an MP3 frame analyzer. This is useful for creating and analyzing
compressed audio files.
    </para>

    &lfs113_checked;

